{"tid":1032092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本王決定著手準備北伐！","createTime":"2019-02-22T06:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T14:42:00.000Z","uid":150100,"like":151,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f30462306fcfb0736de8bdda746fb73993c135","tid":1032092,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"本王屆時將會御駕親征率領大軍先攻上海，再取北京！然後再向西進軍！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeYquak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeYquak.jpg&h=069bb6a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n統一中原之後再派兵遠征高麗<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GAgC4Kh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGAgC4Kh.jpg&h=3c605f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同一時間，朕會再次披甲上陣，帶領大軍進軍東南亞<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqTFh4V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqTFh4V.jpg&h=c8ce216e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n取得東南亞之後再攻打中東同巴爾幹半島<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TkwrX6k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTkwrX6k.jpg&h=0ed6d5e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後就由東歐掃到西歐，再揮軍南歐<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrrGM0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrrGM0p.jpg&h=5fb07f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後再登陸英國<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUWfRsg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUWfRsg.jpg&h=3df3afec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俄國被我國三方包圍下必定投降<br />\n統一歐亞之後朕打算休養生息<br />\n登陸美國和遠征非洲同澳洲之事再作打算"},{"pid":"bb5d0ee5c80f842ff456f68b3e89df51b3176f67","tid":1032092,"uid":130596,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:18:15.000Z","msg":"紙上談兵"},{"pid":"e066f251d503a8bf078243301526f9c51a3bc66e","tid":1032092,"uid":20816,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:18:55.000Z","msg":"精神病發又唔肯睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fca1522ae05fb65a947c86aa800e0ff8af7fc04","tid":1032092,"uid":15010