g src=\"https://na.cx/i/TkwrX6k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTkwrX6k.jpg&h=0ed6d5e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後就由東歐掃到西歐，再揮軍南歐<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrrGM0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrrGM0p.jpg&h=5fb07f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後再登陸英國<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iUWfRsg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiUWfRsg.jpg&h=3df3afec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俄國被我國三方包圍下必定投降<br />\n統一歐亞之後朕打算休養生息<br />\n登陸美國和遠征非洲同澳洲之事再作打算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"返大陸炸村炸省，屌爆晒啲女隻閪"},{"pid":"f8901d121b14c0be5d4d8aaa8a0e7e26055160c1","tid":1032092,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9569e0b987d6e77045e0ca33512ef35bc3df604d","tid":1032092,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"本人可借10萬大軍比閣下"},{"pid":"bc0af9c91275e95ebeb61c124495397f4525b758","tid":1032092,"uid":224860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:25:59.000Z","msg":"統一左次後打算改國號做咩?"},{"pid":"87d85d7fd3c61cc87e13372ebff0fa91e49ab58d","tid":1032092,"uid":150100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9569e0b987d6e77045e0ca33512ef35bc3df604d","tid":1032092,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"本人可借10萬大軍比閣下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"征服台灣嘅任務就交俾你啦"},{"pid":"e06617e40ffbf886c6594df5cb0f637cc399ea4f","tid":1032092,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本人可借10萬大軍比閣下</blockquote>征服台灣嘅任務就交俾你啦，征台大將軍</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f904d40bb3a063f23e6af838d84be52ff73bfec2","tid":1032092,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc0af9c91275e95ebeb61c1